		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Carroll Quigley</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Carroll Quigley</b> (November 9, 1910 – January 3, 1977) was a noted <a href="/wiki/Historian" title="Historian">historian</a>, <a href="/wiki/Polymath" title="Polymath">polymath</a>, and theorist of the <a href="/wiki/Sociocultural_evolution" title="Sociocultural evolution">evolution of civilizations</a>.</p>
